://web.archive.org/web/20120514105935/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/3f482224-2011-11e1-8662-00144feabdc0.html#axzz1fmSrn9yS |dead-url=no }}</ref>和著名的博客作家、社会活动家[[納瓦尼|納瓦尼]]（Alexey Navalny）<ref name=NYer01>Ioffe, Julia, [http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/newsdesk/2011/12/putins-big-mistake.html "Putin’s Big Mistake?"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120907032947/http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/newsdesk/2011/12/putins-big-mistake.html |date=2012-09-07 }}, ''The New Yorker'' blogpost, December 6, 2011. Retrieved 2011-12-06.</ref>。
